metadata.name: Arinishi
metadata.description:
The first explorer of Anymat, the new found world. Arinishi will embark on a dream like adventure in these new lands. What other hero should accompany her? 
Depending on the sale price of Arinishi, a new hero will spawn into Anymat world. 
0.4 - Tahanda, the Shield Wall
0.6 - Narihara, the Flame Avenger
above 0.7 - Mibe, the Bringer of Light
